112
00:05:37.280 --> 00:05:39.280
Oh say me too. That was ironic.

113
00:05:39.280 --> 00:05:42.280
Speaking of grown women, maybe it's time for a little upgrade.

114
00:05:42.280 --> 00:05:47.280
Oh come on. Look at who you've become. You don't need some cliche makeover.

115
00:05:47.280 --> 00:05:52.280
