116
00:05:52.280 --> 00:05:56.280
Aw, Beth, I was joking. Part of my management style.

117
00:05:56.280 --> 00:06:00.280
But isn't comedy just the revelation of an unacknowledged truth?

118
00:06:00.280 --> 00:06:01.280
Think about it.

119
00:06:01.280 --> 00:06:04.280
Let's get out of here girl. You need a blowout.

120
00:06:05.280 --> 00:06:08.280
