145
00:08:01.280 --> 00:08:03.280
I... I just missed them.

146
00:08:03.280 --> 00:08:09.280
You know what, pal? I think that engine snorkel's a good idea. Bottoms up!

147
00:08:09.280 --> 00:08:14.280
Wow, you can really pull that luck off. I could never go short.

148
00:08:14.280 --> 00:08:18.280
It's called disruption. If you don't take risks, you don't grow.

149
00:08:18.280 --> 00:08:20.280
For me, this is pretty bold.

150
00:08:20.280 --> 00:08:23.280
