160
00:08:47.280 --> 00:08:48.280
English Lit.

161
00:08:48.280 --> 00:08:54.280
Beth, I can't make you 17 again, but I can give this gift of knowledge. Life is slipping away.

162
00:08:54.280 --> 00:08:58.280
