167
00:09:06.280 --> 00:09:09.280
Oh, hell yeah! Buy two Rebar, get one free bar?

168
00:09:09.280 --> 00:09:12.280
Matrix, Morty's got an eye for a deal.

169
00:09:13.280 --> 00:09:16.280
I got a hand it to you. This feels pretty good.

170
00:09:16.280 --> 00:09:18.280
Good old American craftsmanship, Morty.

171
00:09:18.280 --> 00:09:20.280
Feels good to use your hands.

172
00:09:21.280 --> 00:09:25.280
Oh, she's purring like an oily little kitten.

173
00:09:26.280 --> 00:09:30.280
Wow, you guys are really spreading out onto the lawn, huh?

174
00:09:30.280 --> 00:09:32.280
Ah, suburbia.

175
00:09:32.280 --> 00:09:34.280
