176
00:09:34.280 --> 00:09:37.280
Listen, if this is about the beers, Morty's cool.

177
00:09:37.280 --> 00:09:39.280
He has like four purple hearts.

178
00:09:39.280 --> 00:09:41.280
Five! Those in a nickel will get you a cup of coffee.

179
00:09:41.280 --> 00:09:44.280
Oh, disillusioned, Morty. Love this guy.

180
00:09:44.280 --> 00:09:47.280
Listen, Beth, if you want to judge someone, call Jerry.

181
00:09:47.280 --> 00:09:49.280
