Because I can't impress upon you.

187
00:10:07.280 --> 00:10:09.280
Oh, my God!

188
00:10:09.280 --> 00:10:11.280
Oh, my God!

189
00:10:11.280 --> 00:10:13.280
Hey, Paul!

190
00:10:13.280 --> 00:10:15.280
No, no! CJ!

191
00:10:15.280 --> 00:10:17.280
Drop block! Marma Duke!

192
00:10:21.280 --> 00:10:24.280
Hey, Paul. He didn't make it.

193
00:10:24.280 --> 00:10:26.280
Wait, we saw you die, man!

194
00:10:26.280 --> 00:10:28.280
I can't.

195
00:10:28.280 --> 00:10:30.280
I can't.

196
00:10:30.280 --> 00:10:32.280
I can't.

197
00:10:32.280 --> 00:10:34.280
I can't.

198
00:10:34.280 --> 00:10:37.280
I got you. I got you.

199
00:10:37.280 --> 00:10:40.280
I can't. I can't die.

200
00:10:40.280 --> 00:10:43.280
I-I got you. I got you.

201
00:10:43.280 --> 00:10:45.280
I can't. I, I can't die!

202
00:10:45.280 --> 00:11:02.280
Ahhh!

203
00:11:02.280 --> 00:11:04.280
Just take whatever you want.

204
00:11:04.280 --> 00:11:06.280
Nothing out here fucking matters.

205
00:11:06.280 --> 00:11:08.280
Wonder who he learned that from.

206
00:11:08.280 --> 00:11:12.280
Probably someone too tamed by neoliberal group think to buy a cool jacket.

207
00:11:12.280 --> 00:11:14.280
Dad, I think maybe you were right on this one.

208
00:11:14.280 --> 00:11:17.280
Beth, that's not how it works. You gotta press it up against their head.

209
