248
00:12:46.280 --> 00:12:48.280
Is that someone you put in a matrix?

249
00:12:48.280 --> 00:12:49.280
Yes!

250
00:12:51.280 --> 00:12:54.280
The seemingly unstoppable and pretty cool looking vehicle

251
00:12:54.280 --> 00:12:57.280
